Package: round
Title: What the Package Does (One Line, Title Case)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Martina", "Sladekova", , "martinasladek@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5059-6576"))
Description: A minimal package that updates the `base::round()` function to get around the floating point problem and round in line with conventions (rounding up for numbers ending in digits 5 or above). Mostly though it's just an excuse for me to learn how to write packages.
